⚙️ 4. APPLICATION LAYER (Execution + Transactions)

Target location: packages/execution/src/flooring/unit-of-measures/

Use Cases:

createUnitOfMeasureUseCase(input: UnitOfMeasureForm):
  normalizedName = domain.normalizeForUniqueness(input.name)
  exists = db.nameExists(normalizedName)
  domain.assertNameAvailable(exists)
  record = db.createRecord(input)
  return record

updateUnitOfMeasureUseCase(id, input: UnitOfMeasureForm):
  normalizedName = domain.normalizeForUniqueness(input.name)
  exists = db.nameExists(normalizedName, excludeId: id)
  domain.assertNameAvailable(exists)
  db.updateRecord(id, input)
  return db.getById(id)

deleteUnitOfMeasureUseCase(id):
  deleteState = db.getDeleteState(id)
  if not found → throw NotFoundError

  domain.assertUOMDeletable({
    categoryLinks: sum of all category count fields,
    serviceLinks: sum of service + template service + work order service counts
  })

  db.deleteRecord(id)
  return { ok: true }

Cross-Cutters:
* Transactions (wrap delete in transaction for safety)
* Idempotency (mutation receipt enforced at transport)
* Error classification (domain errors → AppError)
* Telemetry (withMutationTelemetry at route level)

Rule:
🔥 ALL state mutations pass through Application

