🧠 5. DOMAIN LAYER (Business Rules — Source of Truth)

Target location: packages/domain/src/flooring/unit-of-measures/rules.ts

Current rules (already implemented, need to migrate from features/):

normalizeUnitOfMeasureNameForUniqueness(value: string):
  return value.trim().toLowerCase()

isUnitOfMeasureNameConflict(exists: boolean):
  return exists

isUnitOfMeasureDeleteBlocked({ categoryLinks, serviceLinks }):
  return categoryLinks > 0 || serviceLinks > 0

Rules:
* ❗ Domain has no Prisma imports
* ❗ Domain has no HTTP imports
* ❗ Domain functions are pure — input in, decision out

Why Domain Owns This:
* Prevents UI bypass, API misuse, worker-side violations
* Ensures consistency across ALL entry points
* Testable without any infrastructure

