🔷 7. ERROR HANDLING

Domain Error Shape:
{
  code: "UOM_IN_USE",
  message: "This unit of measure is linked to categories and cannot be deleted",
  status: 409,
}

Error Flow:
Domain throws → Application classifies → Transport normalizes → Controller receives → UI displays

UI Behavior:
* Show error in section (scoped to the action, not the whole page)
* Optionally disable Delete button if known beforehand (query link count on panel open)
* Error dismisses on next user action

