🔥 FINAL PRINCIPLE

UOM is not a simple table.
It is the first fully governed execution path.

This establishes:
* how ALL creates and updates will be validated
* how ALL deletes will be guarded by domain rules
* how ALL record views will be structured under the engine
* how packages/execution, packages/domain, and packages/db relate

